divs: Sighting DetailsAt the time I took the photo I was focused on the jet. I did not notice it until after I pulled the picture up on my computer. I was outside playing with my kids and took a quick shot of the jet flying over head, then I went back to taking photographs of them playing. It may be a bug..I do not know.
